subproject.description:
1) A quantitative inventory of trade and investment complementarities prepared
2) National/subregional business support organizations/brokers engaged to carry out market potential studies and compile company profiles
3) A forum of business support organizations in the subregion organized to define priority product/services on which the project will focus its activities
4) Trade/investment promotion events organized
5) Subregional and/or(when appropriate) Global Compact networks set up
subproject.title: Black Sea Trade and Investment
